divs: Sighting DetailsI'm posting on a UFO sight because the objects where unknown. They were more than likely military aircraft. I wen't outside to smoke, looked up saw an airplane(or what i thought was an airplane) I noticed another,, then another then another then another,, then I walked out to the field,, so i could get a larger range of view of the sky. To my surprise they were EVERYWHERE! At least 40-50 aircraft all flying east,, north east, Not really high in the sky, One flew right over our house. The darkness and fog made it very difficult to see an outline of the craft. I do not think they were alien or something like that. They had solid white light in the front and flashing red lights on both sides of the object. I actually started to panic because I thought something was going on. I immediately ran to the TV to turn on the news waiting for a breaking news story but it never came. I can't find any other information or other people who've had this sighting in my area. I've looked online for any information and there was none. I checked air traffic for commercial aircraft for that hour and there was almost none in my area. Time of sightings: 9:31 PM est, 12-12-2012
